quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Taa Siin, …óen ko Aayeeje Alqur'aanaare nden e Deftere …ďanngunde"
  27,2,Ko nde Peewal e welo-welo wonannde gom…óin…ďe …ďen
  27,3,"∆Āen …ďe no √Īii…ďa e Julde nden …ďe totta Jakka on, hara kam…ďe hi…ďe yananaa fii Laakara on"
  27,4,"Pellet, …ďen …ďe gom…óinaali Laakara on, Men cu…óanii …ďe golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, kam…ďe hi…ďe yinoo"
  27,5,"Ko …ďen woni …ďen, …ďe woodani …óum Lepte bon…óe …óen, kam…ďe ka Laakara ko kam…ďe woni hayru…ďe …ďen"
  27,6,"E pellet, an hi…óa lonnginee Alqur'aanaare nden immorde ka √Ďee√Īo Anndu…óo"
  27,7,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo …ďeynguure makko nden: \"Min dey, mi haynike yiite, aray mi addana on ka nge woni …óon kumpital maa…óum mi addana on docotal hu…ď…ďungal, bela jo'o onon on iwloto"
  27,8,"Tuma nde o arunoo e magge, o noddaa: ∆äum woni barkinaama on won…óo ka yiite e …ďen wonu…ďe banŇče magge, e Senayee wonanii Alla Jooma winndere nden"
  27,9,"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko woni, ko Min woni Alla Teddu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo On"
  27,10,"Li…ďu tuggordu maa…óa ndun, Tuma nde o yi'unoo ndu hindu dilla, a wi'ayma kayru ko ndu mboddi, o hucciti ko o dogu…óo o yiltitaake. Ko an yo Muusaa: \"Wata a hulu, Min dey Nulaa…ďe …ďen hulataa ka Am"
  27,11,"Si wanaa on too√Īu…óo, refti o lontini ko mo∆ī∆īi …ďaawo bone …óen. Pellet, Min ko Mi Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  27,12,"Naadu junngo maa…óa ngon ka jiiba maa…óa, ngo yaltay ko ngo ranewo ko aldaa e bone, […óum no jeyaa] e nder Aayeeje jeenay nulaa…óe e Fir'awna e yim…ďe makko …ďen, pellet, kam…ďe …ďe laatike yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe"
  27,13,"Tuma nde arunoo e ma…ď…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen ko yi'etee…óe, …ďe wi'i: \"∆äu'um, ko mbilewu …ďanngungu"
  27,14,"∆Āe yeddi [Aayeeje …óen], tawi wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin no yananaa fii majje, too√Īe e mawnintinaare. Ndaaru ko honno laatornoo battane fennu…ďe …ďen"